T02TD1744E:111b-1: se danta shr'i yo ga yo gi ni sv'arbh'u ta sam bho gashma sh'a na kalba n'a ma /
T02TD1744E:111b-3: dpal au rgyan gyi rnal 'byor dang rnal 'byor ma'i rang byung gi longs spyod dur khrod kyi rtog pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD1744E:111b-4: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1744E:111b-5: rdo rje rnal 'byor ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1744E:111b-6: shar gyi dur khrod dbang po gtum drag dpag tshad bcu gnyis khor yug la /
T02TD1744E:111b-7: dpag tshad lnga zheng du gnas pa /
T02TD1744E:112a-0: @112a * // dbyibs ni shing rta rkang pa gsum pa lta bu /
T02TD1744E:112a-1: gtso bo klu sgrub snying pos byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1744E:112a-2: shing ni gser mdog lo ma brgyar gyis shing //
T02TD1744E:112a-3: zhing skyong dkar po gri thod glang chen gdong //
T02TD1744E:112a-4: phyogs skyong brgya byin glang chen gdan rigs bcas //
T02TD1744E:112a-5: rdo rje mkha' 'gro pre ta yi dags za //
T02TD1744E:112a-6: byang chub chen po'i mchod rten gyis sa 'dzin //
T02TD1744E:112a-7: mtha' yas sngon po'i klu ni 'dud byed cing //
T02TD1744E:112a-8: thod pa brtsegs pa'i spyil bus kun bkang zhing //
T02TD1744E:112a-9: de na rnal 'byor pa'i rgyal po a'arya de ba la sogs pa shin tu mang ba bzhugs so //
T02TD1744E:112a-10: rnal 'byor ma ni mdzes ma dang snying stobs can ma la sogs pa'o //
T02TD1744E:112a-11: de dag ni rgyud gsang 'dus kyi rjes su 'jug cing klu sgrub yid la byed pa'o //
T02TD1744E:112a-12: lho'i dur khrod gshin rje 'bar ba'i nags tshal /
T02TD1744E:112a-13: dpag tshad drug cu gnyis khor yug / dpag tshad bco lnga rgyang grags gcig / dbyibs ni 'khor lo 'dra /
T02TD1744E:112a-14: dombi he ru ka yis byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1744E:112a-15: bee d'ur+ya mdog lo ma brgyar gyes shing //
T02TD1744E:112a-16: zhing skyong nag po gri thod ma he gdong //
T02TD1744E:112a-17: phyogs skyong gshin rje ma he'i gdan rigs bcas //
T02TD1744E:112a-18: rin chen mkha' 'gro kang ka dbang bskur byed //
T02TD1744E:112a-19: cho 'phrul ston pa'i mchod rten gyis sa 'dzin //
T02TD1744E:112a-20: dung skyong dkar po'i klu ni 'dud par byed //
T02TD1744E:112a-21: thod pa rus pa dum bu'i spyil bus bkang //
T02TD1744E:112a-22: rnal 'byor pa ni aa wa dh'u t'i dang /
T02TD1744E:112a-25: gshin rje gshed nag po'i rjes su 'jug cing dombi he ru ka yid la byed do //
T02TD1744E:112a-26: nub kyi dur khrod chu bdag thod pa can dpag tshad bzhi bcu brgyad khor yug la /
T02TD1744E:112a-27: dpag tshad bcu gnyis zheng du gnas /
T02TD1744E:112a-28: dbyibs ni ban lang spyod lta bu zlum po ste /
T02TD1744E:112a-29: mkhas pa rta dbyangs kyis ni byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1744E:112a-30: shing ni byi ru'i mdog can lo 'dab rgyas //
T02TD1744E:112a-31: zhing skyong dmar po gri thod chu srin gdong ;
T02TD1744E:112a-32: / phyogs skyong chu lha chu srin gdan rigs bcas //
T02TD1744E:112a-33: padma mkha' 'gro chos ston kun dha ra //
T02TD1744E:112a-34: lha las babs pa'i mchod rten gyis sa 'dzin //
T02TD1744E:112a-35: dmar po dga' bo'i klu rnams 'dud byed cing //
T02TD1744E:112a-36: ro rnams brtsegs pa'i spyil bus kun bkang zhing //
T02TD1744E:112b-0: de ni rnal 'byor @112b pa ni ku ku ri pa dang /
T02TD1744E:112b-1: rnal 'byor ma ni snying po'i rgyan ma dang /
T02TD1744E:112b-2: de dag thams cad ni rgyud sgyu 'phrul chen mo'i rjes su 'jug cing slob dpon rta dbyangs yid la byed pa'o //
T02TD1744E:112b-3: byang gi dur khrod lus ngan 'jigs byed dang //
T02TD1744E:112b-4: dpag tshad brgyad cu pa khor yug la /
T02TD1744E:112b-5: dpag tshad nyi shu zheng du gnas /
T02TD1744E:112b-6: dbyibs ni shing rta rkang pa bzhi pa lta bu /
T02TD1744E:112b-7: slob dpon padma can gyis byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1744E:112b-8: ma rgad ljang mdog lo ma brgyar gyis shing //
T02TD1744E:112b-9: zhing skyong ljang gu gri thod khyu mchog gdong //
T02TD1744E:112b-10: phyogs skyong gnod sbyin khyu mchog gdan rigs bcas //
T02TD1744E:112b-11: las kyi mkha' 'gro las 'byor dam tshig la //
T02TD1744E:112b-12: bkra shis brtsegs pa'i mchod rten gyis sa 'dzin //
T02TD1744E:112b-13: ljang gu karko ta yi klu rab 'dud //
T02TD1744E:112b-14: ro yi spyil bus kun nas bkang ba'i zhing //
T02TD1744E:112b-15: de na rnal 'byor pa ni bzang po dang /
T02TD1744E:112b-16: rnal 'byor ma ni brdung ma la sogs pa'o //
T02TD1744E:112b-17: de dag rgyud dgyes pa rdo rje'i rjes su 'jug cing slob dpon mtsho skyes rjes su dran par byed do //
T02TD1744E:112b-18: shar lho'i dur khrod me mtshams dpal 'dren dpag tshad bcu gnyis khor yug la /
T02TD1744E:112b-19: dpag tshad gsum ni zheng du gnas /
T02TD1744E:112b-20: dbyibs ni skyes pa gzhon nu'i lag mthil lta bu ste /
T02TD1744E:112b-21: gtso bo sa ra ha yis byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1744E:112b-22: shing ni aa mra'i mdog can lo 'dab rgyas //
T02TD1744E:112b-23: zhing skyong ser po gri thod ra skyes gdong //
T02TD1744E:112b-24: phyogs skyong me lha ra skyes gdan rigs bcas //
T02TD1744E:112b-25: sna tshogs mkha' 'gro ro langs sbyin sreg byed //
T02TD1744E:112b-26: padma spungs pa'i mchod rten gyis sa 'dzin //
T02TD1744E:112b-27: dkar po padma chen po'i klu rab 'dud //
T02TD1744E:112b-28: yi dags ro yi spyil bus kun bkang zhing //
T02TD1744E:112b-29: de na rnal 'byor pa ni ghu na ka na ka dang /
T02TD1744E:112b-30: rnal 'byor ma ni padma rdo rje la sogs pa'o //
T02TD1744E:112b-31: de dag ni rgyud bde mchog 'khor lo'i rjes su 'jug cing dpal sa ra ha pa rjes su dran par byed pa'o //
T02TD1744E:112b-32: lho nub kyi dur khrod dbang ldan ha ha sgrogs zhes pa dpag tshad drug khor yug la /
T02TD1744E:112b-33: dpag tshad bzhi ni zheng du gnas /
T02TD1744E:112b-34: dbyibs ni padma dkar po kha bye ba lta bu ste /
T02TD1744E:112b-35: dpal mchog nag po zhabs kyis byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1744E:112b-36: aindra n'i la'i shing ni lo 'dab rgyas //
T02TD1744E:113a-2: phyogs skyong srin po yi dags gdan rigs bcas //
T02TD1744E:113a-3: dam tshig mkha' 'gro kyang rnams nye bar ston //
T02TD1744E:113a-4: bdud 'dul chen po'i mchod rten gyis sa 'dzin //
T02TD1744E:113a-5: gzi can dkar dmar mdog can klu rab 'dud //
T02TD1744E:113a-6: keng rus yi dags lo ma'i spyil bus gang //
T02TD1744E:113a-7: de na rnal 'byor pa ni bram ze stobs can gyi bu rnal 'byor pa gser mdog can dang /
T02TD1744E:113a-8: rnal 'byor ma ni bzhin khro ma la sogs pa'o //
T02TD1744E:113a-9: de dag ni rgyud snying po gnyis dang /
T02TD1744E:113a-10: rta mchog gi rgyud kyi rjes su 'jug cing dpal nag po zhabs rjes su dran par byed do //
T02TD1744E:113a-11: nub byang dur khrod bden bral mun chen zhes pa dpag tshad bcu bzhi pa khor yug la /
T02TD1744E:113a-12: dpag tshad bcu gnyis zheng du gnas /
T02TD1744E:113a-13: dbyibs ni chu'i ri mo 'khyil ba lta bu ste /
T02TD1744E:113a-14: mkhas pa ku ku ri pas byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1744E:113a-15: shel gyi mdog can shing ni lo 'dab rgyas //
T02TD1744E:113a-16: zhing skyong sngon po gri thod sha ba'i mdog / phyogs skyong rlung lha sha ba'i gdan rigs bcas //
T02TD1744E:113a-17: thams cad mkha' 'gro gsang ba'i chos ston cing //
T02TD1744E:113a-18: gtsug phud dag pa'i mchod rten gyis sa 'dzin //
T02TD1744E:113a-19: padma dkar po'i klu ni rab tu 'dud //
T02TD1744E:113a-20: rtsva spyil rus pa'i rgyan spras kyis gang zhing //
T02TD1744E:113a-21: de na rnal 'byor pa ni rgyun tu zhugs pa dang /
T02TD1744E:113a-22: rnal 'byor ma ni zhing la sogs pa'o //
T02TD1744E:113a-23: de dag ni rgyud rnal 'byor ma'i rjes su 'jug cing dpal ku ku ri rjes su dran par byed do //
T02TD1744E:113a-24: byang shar gyi dur khrod rlung du ca co sgrogs zhes pa dpag tshad nyi shu khor yug la /
T02TD1744E:113a-25: dpag chad lnga ni zheng du gnas /
T02TD1744E:113a-26: dbyibs ni dge slong gi lhung bzed lta bu ste /
T02TD1744E:113a-27: mkha' 'gro rdo rje phag mos byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1744E:113a-28: rin chen dung mdog shing ni lo 'dab rgyas //
T02TD1744E:113a-29: zhing skyong dkar sham gri thod rta yi gdong //
T02TD1744E:113a-30: phyogs skyong 'byung po rta yi gdan rigs bcas //
T02TD1744E:113a-31: 'jig rten mkha' 'gro bskyod cing gtor ma 'dzin //
T02TD1744E:113a-32: chos kyi 'khor lo'i mchod rten gyis sa 'dzin //
T02TD1744E:113a-33: nor 'dzin na ros mdog can klu rab 'dud //
T02TD1744E:113a-34: so phag ba rtsegs pa'i spyil bus kun bkang zhing //
T02TD1744E:113a-35: de na rnal 'byor pa ni dpal he ru ka pa dang /
T02TD1744E:113b-0: rnal 'byor ma ni bdag med ma dang bdud rtsi ma la sogs @113b pa'o ;
T02TD1744E:113b-1: / de ni rgyud m'a h'a m'a ya nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rjes su 'jug cing rdo rje phag mo rjes su dran par byed do //
T02TD1744E:113b-2: dpal au rgyan gyi rnal 'byor pa dang rnal 'byor ma'i rang byung gi longs spyod dur khrod kyi rtog pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD1744E:113b-3: slob dpon birla [*birwa?] pas mdzad pa las btus pa /
T02TD1744E:113b-4: rnal 'byor pa pradzny'a shr'i dzny'a na k'irtis rang 'gyur du mdzad pa'o//
